ygData.messageBody:
found the info on the Everworld.net site....

FIRST ENCHANTER TO 50 (AT LEAST I THINK SO) 7:08PM PST- Kellindil
Another member of the Fires of Heaven member guild has reached level 50.
Zamtil Litmaz, the gnomish enchanter, got it earlier today. He's the first
enchanter to reach 50 that I know of. Here's a screenshot of him in his
spiffy new robe: Zamtil

ps. any enchanters on The Rathe server that would like to group with me?
I've only ONCE grouped with a fellow enchanter and would enjoy the
commisserable.

Fistlebane, High Elf Enchanter of the 12th level. ...currently slumming
around Freeport/Commonlands area.
